<br>
Retriving the ink bottle from the enchanter guild leader in the Temple Bertoxx in Qeynos.<br>
<br>
She does not like me. Eight times over she doesn't like me.  I quote: &quot;DIE like a motherless gnolll!&quot;, which whether I agree with this association or not, I do.<br>
<br>
There are many explanations for this...but the most compelling is:<br>
I am a Karana worshipping High Elf. <br>
<br>
From what I have learned from a follower of Bertoxx, the Temple of Thunder is leading the Inquisition into the plague. Only followers of Rodecet are more hated. Grand. Frankly, having spent time in Qeynos, they ought welcome a good lightning strike, get a genetic do-over.<br>
<br>
I have tried going in as the following illusions: Human, Dark Elf and werewolf, as other enchanters have said works for them. She and her minions saw through me like Section-8 window panes. <br>
<br>
