<br>
As they're trainers, I doubt they can be killed, no matter what forces I could muster. Though I would like to very VERY much. <br>
<br>
Again, as trainers, I doubt I could pacify the mage and wiz and then charm the enchantress. They're immune to such games, yes?<br>
<br>
After my first failures, (1-5, due to see invis guards), I started drinking with a guard in Karana, hoping to gain favor with the Blood Sabres. I've spent about 100pp so far, in 5gp increments. Very tedious, but not an all bad way to enjoy the afternoon. Is this my best bet?<br>
<br>
Or, as I am very concerned may be the case, am I simply &quot;screwed&quot; due to my deity?<br>
<br>
Many thanks and best wishes for enchanted dreams,<br>
