<br>
Now, it all depends on your convictions.   Are you willing to bite the bullet and ruin your faction with most of Qeynos?<br>
<br>
If so, here's the way:<br>
Go to Blackburrow.  Zone in from Qeynos Hills.  As you enter the wide open area, there is something looking like a hollow tree trunk to your left.  Go inside.   It has a fake floor, and you'll fall through.<br>
